# Go stdlib CVE in pre-built third-party binaries (gh, blogwatcher, camsnap, etc.)
# These are downloaded from upstream GitHub releases — we cannot recompile them.
# Will be resolved when upstream projects rebuild with Go >= 1.25.7
CVE-2025-68121

